      "raw_text": "AT the chamber OF commerce at\nnoon today F. B. Wright made a\nmotion that a vote of thanks be\nrendered to Mayor Daggett for his\nprompt quelling Of the strike dis\nturbances on the corner of River\nside av. and Howard st. David T..\nHam, who has been mentioned as\nan opponent Of the mayor, made a\nsubstitution motion that Wright's\nmotion be tabled. Hams motion\ncarried"
